=== 國家隊 ===
艾殊利·威廉斯透過其[[威爾斯人|威爾斯]][[祖父|祖父]]而獲得代表[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯國家隊]]的資格。2008年3月17日由於[[基斯·根達|根達]]需要為[[威爾斯21歲以下足球代表隊|威爾斯U21]]出戰，艾殊利·威廉斯獲首次徵召加入國家隊備戰作客對[[盧森堡國家足球隊|盧森堡]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7299657.stm |title=Key players out of Wales friendly |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-03-17 |accessdate=2011-01-11 |archive-date=2019-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204143421/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7299657.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於3月26日獲派正選上陣，協助球隊2-0取勝奏凱而回<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7309955.stm |title=Luxembourg 0-2 Wales |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2008-03-26 |accessdate=2011-01-11 |archive-date=2019-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190917154425/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7309955.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年11月14日威爾斯在[[卡迪夫城運動場|卡迪夫城運動場]]首次舉行國際賽[[友誼賽|友賽]][[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]，[[克雷格·贝拉米|比拿美]]及[[詹姆斯·科林斯|占士·哥連斯]]因傷缺陣，時任領隊[[約翰·陶錫|陶錫]]委任艾殊利·威廉斯首次擔任[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]之職<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Swansea-s-Ashley-Williams-braced-to-lead-Wales-out-at-Cardiff-ground-article220845.html |title=Swansea's Ashley Williams braced to lead Wales out at Cardiff ground |publisher=''mirrorfootball.co.uk'' |date=2009-11-13 |accessdate=2011-01-11}}</ref>，他不負所託，協助球隊大勝3-0<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8344879.stm |title=Wales 3-0 Scotland |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-11-14 |accessdate=2011-01-11 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109005334/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8344879.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

